WITH
SQ_Pif30Stage AS (
	SELECT
		Pif30StageId,
		ExtractDate,
		SourceSystemId,
		AuditId,
		PerPifSymbol,
		PerPifpolicyNumber,
		PerPifModule,
		PerId,
		PerUse,
		PerSequenceNumber,
		PerAmendmentNumber,
		PerEnteredDate,
		PerDescLine1,
		PerDescline2,
		PerDescline3,
		PerStatus,
		PerOriginalRatebook,
		PerRatebook,
		PerEndorsementPrem,
		PerH390firerb,
		PerH390ecrb,
		PerH390vmmrb,
		Pif30Filler,
		PerPmsfutureuse,
		PerACAFixedidentifier2,
		PerExistInscreditdate,
		PerLpidnumber,
		PerHOBMunitverb,
		PerHOBMunit,
		PerHBBMseq,
		PerInhomeBusDesc,
		PerLPIDNumberOld,
		PerYr2000custuse,
		PerDuplicateKeySequence
	FROM Pif30Stage
),
EXP_VALUES AS (
	SELECT
	Pif30StageId,
	ExtractDate,
	SourceSystemId,
	AuditId,
	PerPifSymbol,
	PerPifpolicyNumber,
	PerPifModule,
	PerId,
	PerUse,
	PerSequenceNumber,
	PerAmendmentNumber,
	PerEnteredDate,
	PerDescLine1,
	PerDescline2,
	PerDescline3,
	PerStatus,
	PerOriginalRatebook,
	PerRatebook,
	PerEndorsementPrem,
	PerH390firerb,
	PerH390ecrb,
	PerH390vmmrb,
	Pif30Filler,
	PerPmsfutureuse,
	PerACAFixedidentifier2,
	PerExistInscreditdate,
	PerLpidnumber,
	PerHOBMunitverb,
	PerHOBMunit,
	PerHBBMseq,
	PerInhomeBusDesc,
	PerLPIDNumberOld,
	PerYr2000custuse,
	PerDuplicateKeySequence
	FROM SQ_Pif30Stage
),
ArchPif30Stage AS (
	INSERT INTO ArchPif30Stage
	(Pif30StageId, ExtractDate, SourceSystemId, AuditId, PerPifSymbol, PerPifpolicyNumber, PerPifModule, PerId, PerUse, PerSequenceNumber, PerAmendmentNumber, PerEnteredDate, PerDescLine1, PerDescline2, PerDescline3, PerStatus, PerOriginalRatebook, PerRatebook, PerEndorsementPrem, PerH390firerb, PerH390ecrb, PerH390vmmrb, Pif30Filler, PerPmsfutureuse, PerACAFixedidentifier2, PerExistInscreditdate, PerLpidnumber, PerHOBMunitverb, PerHOBMunit, PerHBBMseq, PerInhomeBusDesc, PerLPIDNumberOld, PerYr2000custuse, PerDuplicateKeySequence)
	SELECT 
	PIF30STAGEID, 
	EXTRACTDATE, 
	SOURCESYSTEMID, 
	AUDITID, 
	PERPIFSYMBOL, 
	PERPIFPOLICYNUMBER, 
	PERPIFMODULE, 
	PERID, 
	PERUSE, 
	PERSEQUENCENUMBER, 
	PERAMENDMENTNUMBER, 
	PERENTEREDDATE, 
	PERDESCLINE1, 
	PERDESCLINE2, 
	PERDESCLINE3, 
	PERSTATUS, 
	PERORIGINALRATEBOOK, 
	PERRATEBOOK, 
	PERENDORSEMENTPREM, 
	PERH390FIRERB, 
	PERH390ECRB, 
	PERH390VMMRB, 
	PIF30FILLER, 
	PERPMSFUTUREUSE, 
	PERACAFIXEDIDENTIFIER2, 
	PEREXISTINSCREDITDATE, 
	PERLPIDNUMBER, 
	PERHOBMUNITVERB, 
	PERHOBMUNIT, 
	PERHBBMSEQ, 
	PERINHOMEBUSDESC, 
	PERLPIDNUMBEROLD, 
	PERYR2000CUSTUSE, 
	PERDUPLICATEKEYSEQUENCE
	FROM EXP_VALUES
),
